              child: child,
            ),
          ),
          child: Container(
            width: gridPx,
            height: gridPx,
            decoration: BoxDecoration(
              color: AppColors.gridBg,
              borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(20),
              border: Border.all(
                  color: AppColors.accent.withOpacity(0.25), width: 1.5),
              boxShadow: [
                BoxShadow(
